document_data.name: Bell Lane
document_data.mainbody: '''Bell Lane''' was a street in the built-up area of [[Hultail]] in [[Cormyr]].
document_data.Geography: Bell Lane was a curved street that moved from north to south in the southwestern part of Hultail. In the 15{{th}} century [[DR]], Bell Lane was where the cobbler shop of [[Arlburt Nammond]] was located.
